&lt;Candlewood Bank and TrustCo> said it plans an initial public offering of 500,000 commonshares at an expected price of 10 dlrs each through underwriterMoseley Holdings Corp &lt;MOSE>, which has been granted an optionto buy up to 75,000 more shares to cover overallotments.    Candlewood is being formed to serve the area aroundCandlewood Lake in Connecitcut,  Proceeds from the offeringwould support its operations. Reuter&#3;